title: Tournelon Blanc
text: The Tournelon Blanc is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> of the Swiss <a href="Pennine%20Alps">Pennine Alps</a>, overlooking the <a href="Lac%20de%20Mauvoisin">lake of Mauvoisin</a> in the canton of <a href="Valais">Valais</a>. It belongs to the <a href="Grand%20Combin">Grand Combin</a> massif and lies east of the <a href="Corbassi%C3%A8re%20Glacier">Corbassière Glacier</a>.
